WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.700 line:80%
=Episode 29=

00:01:38.650 --> 00:01:39.540 line:80%
Uncle Xue,

00:01:41.210 --> 00:01:42.420 line:80%
what kind of person

00:01:43.370 --> 00:01:44.850 line:80%
was Mu Zhengyang, really?

00:01:47.090 --> 00:01:47.930 line:80%
Zhengyang was...

00:01:50.010 --> 00:01:50.850 line:80%
He...

00:01:51.460 --> 00:01:52.650 line:80%
It's been so many years.

00:01:53.570 --> 00:01:55.090 line:80%
What's there left to hide?

00:02:02.420 --> 00:02:03.620 line:80%
The first time I saw him, he had

00:02:04.900 --> 00:02:06.010 line:80%
(Little Mu Zhengyang)
no family, no home,

00:02:06.010 --> 00:02:07.210 line:80%
just wandering,

00:02:07.210 --> 00:02:09.490 line:80%
fighting dogs for scraps like an animal.

00:02:10.090 --> 00:02:12.140 line:80%
He could barely speak in full sentences.

00:02:23.140 --> 00:02:24.140 line:80%
The village kids

00:02:25.460 --> 00:02:26.740 line:80%
called him a mongrel.

00:02:27.150 --> 00:02:28.020 line:80%
Mongrel!

00:02:28.020 --> 00:02:29.580 line:80%
Nobody wants you!

00:02:29.900 --> 00:02:30.860 line:80%
Little mongrel!

00:02:30.860 --> 00:02:31.970 line:80%
You're not fit to play with us.

00:02:31.970 --> 00:02:32.810 line:80%
Get him!

00:02:33.090 --> 00:02:34.340 line:80%
They were cruel, those kids.,

00:02:34.340 --> 00:02:35.340 line:80%
always picking on him.

00:02:36.180 --> 00:02:37.340 line:80%
But he never broke.

00:02:37.340 --> 00:02:38.460 line:80%
He wouldn't bow to them.

00:02:39.090 --> 00:02:40.690 line:80%
They'd beat him until he bled,

00:02:41.620 --> 00:02:42.460 line:80%
but his eyes

00:02:43.410 --> 00:02:44.810 line:80%
stayed fierce, like a cornered wolf's.

00:02:47.930 --> 00:02:50.410 line:80%
One day, I couldn't just watch.

00:02:51.740 --> 00:02:52.900 line:80%
I stepped in.

00:02:53.860 --> 00:02:55.620 line:80%
- Little mongrel!
Bad guys, bad guys!

00:02:55.620 --> 00:02:56.460 line:80%
- Run! Run!
- Bad guys!

00:02:58.370 --> 00:02:59.300 line:80%
You okay?

00:03:06.860 --> 00:03:07.700 line:80%
Come here.

00:03:08.780 --> 00:03:10.300 line:80%
Good boy. Hang in there.

00:03:16.740 --> 00:03:17.580 line:80%
My mother

00:03:18.620 --> 00:03:19.620 line:80%
saw him, took pity,

00:03:20.530 --> 00:03:21.530 line:80%
took him in.

00:03:22.490 --> 00:03:23.490 line:80%
Careful now.

00:03:30.900 --> 00:03:31.740 line:80%
Easy.

00:03:35.690 --> 00:03:36.530 line:80%
Go on, eat.

00:03:38.340 --> 00:03:40.180 line:80%
But the good times didn't last.

00:03:42.060 --> 00:03:42.970 line:80%
My father

00:03:44.180 --> 00:03:45.340 line:80%
had a hunting accident.

00:03:46.210 --> 00:03:48.900 line:80%
Then the village bullies set their sights
on us.

00:03:49.970 --> 00:03:51.140 line:80%
One night,

00:03:53.930 --> 00:03:55.900 line:80%
they broke in.

00:04:08.740 --> 00:04:10.090 line:80%
Come here. Come on.

00:04:11.530 --> 00:04:12.620 line:80%
Hold still.

00:04:22.650 --> 00:04:23.780 line:80%
You animal!

00:04:24.580 --> 00:04:25.420 line:80%
Let go!

00:04:25.900 --> 00:04:26.740 line:80%
Come on!

00:04:29.580 --> 00:04:30.900 line:80%
No!

00:04:32.290 --> 00:04:33.610 line:80%
Mother!

00:04:35.210 --> 00:04:37.090 line:80%
Mother!

00:04:37.090 --> 00:04:39.900 line:80%
Mother, wake up!

00:04:39.900 --> 00:04:41.380 line:80%
Mother!

00:04:42.210 --> 00:04:43.530 line:80%
Mother!

00:04:44.820 --> 00:04:47.500 line:80%
Please wake up!

00:04:47.500 --> 00:04:49.410 line:80%
Mother!

00:04:55.140 --> 00:04:56.460 line:80%
Mother!

00:04:58.020 --> 00:04:59.850 line:80%
Mother!

00:04:59.850 --> 00:05:01.380 line:80%
Wake up, Mother.

00:05:04.210 --> 00:05:06.410 line:80%
Please wake up.

00:05:11.090 --> 00:05:12.410 line:80%
Mother!

00:05:14.140 --> 00:05:15.460 line:80%
Mother!

00:05:25.340 --> 00:05:26.180 line:80%
Zhengyang.

00:05:31.700 --> 00:05:33.970 line:80%
I have to avenge her.

00:05:45.730 --> 00:05:47.140 line:80%
Some preyed on the helpless

00:05:48.700 --> 00:05:49.940 line:80%
and the others stood there and watched.

00:05:51.700 --> 00:05:52.700 line:80%
Zhengyang said

00:05:53.730 --> 00:05:55.900 line:80%
they all deserve to die for what they did.

00:06:05.170 --> 00:06:06.140 line:80%
What happened then?

00:06:08.090 --> 00:06:09.020 line:80%
After that,

00:06:11.820 --> 00:06:13.380 line:80%
we wandered,

00:06:14.050 --> 00:06:15.210 line:80%
just the two of us.

00:06:16.170 --> 00:06:17.290 line:80%
Until one day, we ran into

00:06:18.170 --> 00:06:19.650 line:80%
someone from the martial world.

00:06:28.420 --> 00:06:30.860 line:80%
(Young Mu Zhengyang)

00:06:36.820 --> 00:06:37.660 line:80%
Water...

00:06:37.900 --> 00:06:38.740 line:80%
Please...

00:06:38.940 --> 00:06:39.900 line:80%
Give me water...

00:06:45.340 --> 00:06:46.290 line:80%
Young Master?

00:06:47.210 --> 00:06:48.500 line:80%
What are you doing here?

00:06:49.340 --> 00:06:51.580 line:80%
You're the heir to the Li Sect.

00:06:52.140 --> 00:06:54.460 line:80%
Get back to the Hanhai Mountains now.

00:07:02.820 --> 00:07:03.660 line:80%
Zhengyang

00:07:04.170 --> 00:07:05.410 line:80%
decided to join the Li Sect.

00:07:06.650 --> 00:07:08.020 line:80%
He had these fragments

00:07:08.290 --> 00:07:09.140 line:80%
from when he was little

00:07:09.780 --> 00:07:10.820 line:80%
and someone feeding him

00:07:11.380 --> 00:07:12.340 line:80%
and holding him.

00:07:13.500 --> 00:07:15.410 line:80%
And there was another child like him.

00:07:15.410 --> 00:07:16.290 line:80%
Maybe that child

00:07:17.460 --> 00:07:18.940 line:80%
was the one they called

00:07:20.290 --> 00:07:21.130 line:80%
Young Master.

00:07:35.380 --> 00:07:36.700 line:80%
Maybe you shouldn't go.

00:07:37.340 --> 00:07:38.820 line:80%
They say those people from the Demon Sect

00:07:38.820 --> 00:07:40.090 line:80%
are savages who would eat you alive.

00:07:40.410 --> 00:07:41.250 line:80%
I have to.

00:07:41.940 --> 00:07:43.020 line:80%
I need to know

00:07:43.020 --> 00:07:43.940 line:80%
who I am.

00:07:44.610 --> 00:07:45.450 line:80%
Youfu,

00:07:45.780 --> 00:07:46.620 line:80%
go back

00:07:47.530 --> 00:07:48.370 line:80%
and wait for me.

00:07:50.700 --> 00:07:51.540 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:07:52.140 --> 00:07:53.290 line:80%
I'll come back alive.

00:08:16.290 --> 00:08:17.380 line:80%
Years later,

00:08:18.050 --> 00:08:19.090 line:80%
he came back.

00:08:19.650 --> 00:08:21.140 line:80%
He was totally different then.

00:08:23.940 --> 00:08:24.780 line:80%
Youfu!

00:08:26.340 --> 00:08:27.290 line:80%
Zhengyang!

00:08:34.410 --> 00:08:35.570 line:80%
Let me look at you!

00:08:37.690 --> 00:08:38.900 line:80%
Sit down,

00:08:41.140 --> 00:08:41.980 line:80%
let me

00:08:41.980 --> 00:08:42.930 line:80%
get you something to eat.

00:08:48.530 --> 00:08:49.370 line:80%
Zhengyang,

00:08:50.330 --> 00:08:51.220 line:80%
what is that

00:08:51.570 --> 00:08:52.740 line:80%
on your back?

00:08:52.740 --> 00:08:54.290 line:80%
What did they do to you?

00:08:57.050 --> 00:08:57.890 line:80%
Youfu,

00:08:58.410 --> 00:08:59.250 line:80%
don't worry.

00:08:59.810 --> 00:09:01.220 line:80%
Everyone who ever hurt me,

00:09:02.100 --> 00:09:03.690 line:80%
I'll make them pay.

00:09:04.290 --> 00:09:06.290 line:80%
You... you're going back?

00:09:06.290 --> 00:09:07.130 line:80%
Of course.

00:09:08.330 --> 00:09:10.810 line:80%
I'm going to take back what's mine.

00:09:13.810 --> 00:09:16.290 line:80%
There's no justice in this world.

00:09:17.810 --> 00:09:19.450 line:80%
So I'll

00:09:20.100 --> 00:09:21.570 line:80%
make my own.

00:09:22.050 --> 00:09:22.890 line:80%
That time,

00:09:23.410 --> 00:09:25.050 line:80%
he'd changed.

00:09:25.050 --> 00:09:25.900 line:80%
He said

00:09:25.900 --> 00:09:27.050 line:80%
he had a complicated identity.

00:09:27.290 --> 00:09:28.450 line:80%
Once he reclaimed his birthright,

00:09:28.690 --> 00:09:30.020 line:80%
he'd tell me everything.

00:09:31.780 --> 00:09:32.740 line:80%
And then?

00:09:33.810 --> 00:09:35.620 line:80%
We met one more time.

00:09:35.620 --> 00:09:36.570 line:80%
When he came

00:09:38.380 --> 00:09:40.140 line:80%
to talk to you about the engagement?

00:09:40.530 --> 00:09:41.370 line:80%
Yes.

00:09:43.410 --> 00:09:44.250 line:80%
That night,

00:09:44.570 --> 00:09:45.620 line:80%
he talked and talked.

00:09:46.330 --> 00:09:49.410 line:80%
For once, he seemed to have hope.

00:09:49.410 --> 00:09:50.290 line:80%
But then he said

00:09:50.930 --> 00:09:52.690 line:80%
he'd hurt Pingshu.

00:09:52.690 --> 00:09:54.620 line:80%
He was terrified she wouldn't forgive him.

00:09:54.620 --> 00:09:56.170 line:80%
He couldn't bring himself to tell her

00:09:56.170 --> 00:09:58.140 line:80%
what he really was.

00:09:58.140 --> 00:10:00.220 line:80%
He was afraid she'd leave him.

00:10:00.220 --> 00:10:02.100 line:80%
His whole life was suffering.

00:10:03.650 --> 00:10:04.930 line:80%
Bullied as a kid,

00:10:05.570 --> 00:10:07.050 line:80%
he never learned to trust anyone.

00:10:07.450 --> 00:10:09.290 line:80%
He finally met Ms. Cai, but even then,

00:10:10.330 --> 00:10:12.100 line:80%
he couldn't give her his whole heart.

00:10:12.860 --> 00:10:13.900 line:80%
In the end, that poor man

00:10:14.740 --> 00:10:16.050 line:80%
died without even knowing why.

00:10:16.690 --> 00:10:17.530 line:80%
No one

00:10:20.020 --> 00:10:21.220 line:80%
even knows where his body is.

00:10:21.860 --> 00:10:22.860 line:80%
I don't feel sorry for him at all.

00:10:25.380 --> 00:10:26.220 line:80%
Young Master.

00:10:28.380 --> 00:10:29.980 line:80%
Mu Zhengyang's hands were dripping with blood.

00:10:30.410 --> 00:10:31.570 line:80%
He killed plenty who deserved it

00:10:31.570 --> 00:10:32.650 line:80%
and plenty who didn't.

00:10:33.020 --> 00:10:34.780 line:80%
He turned this whole martial world upside down,

00:10:35.530 --> 00:10:36.900 line:80%
and my father got caught up in the wreckage.

00:10:37.900 --> 00:10:39.860 line:80%
If he ended up in hell,

00:10:39.860 --> 00:10:40.780 line:80%
good riddance.

00:10:41.050 --> 00:10:42.140 line:80%
Young Master,

00:10:42.140 --> 00:10:44.410 line:80%
I was just chatting with Miss Cai.

00:10:50.290 --> 00:10:51.140 line:80%
Let me show you something.

00:11:00.450 --> 00:11:01.740 line:80%
When did you plant this?

00:11:02.650 --> 00:11:03.930 line:80%
After you and Song Yuzhi left.

00:11:04.860 --> 00:11:05.700 line:80%
That long ago?

00:11:09.140 --> 00:11:09.980 line:80%
Zhao,

00:11:11.900 --> 00:11:13.530 line:80%
if you ever miss home,

00:11:13.530 --> 00:11:14.690 line:80%
just come here and take a look.

00:11:26.930 --> 00:11:27.770 line:80%
Mu Qingyan.

00:11:29.290 --> 00:11:30.740 line:80%
I want to give you something too.

00:11:32.500 --> 00:11:33.340 line:80%
Alright.

00:11:54.980 --> 00:11:57.100 line:80%
Mu Qingyan's taken over the Bliss Palace.

00:11:57.810 --> 00:11:59.290 line:80%
Why isn't Zhao back yet?

00:11:59.980 --> 00:12:01.980 line:80%
Our dear junior sister, that traitor,

00:12:01.980 --> 00:12:03.450 line:80%
finally got what she wanted.

00:12:03.450 --> 00:12:04.450 line:80%
She's the wife of the Chief now.

00:12:04.860 --> 00:12:05.700 line:80%
Why would she ever come back?

00:12:06.330 --> 00:12:07.170 line:80%
Enough.

00:12:08.220 --> 00:12:09.060 line:80%
Just stop.

00:12:09.810 --> 00:12:10.650 line:80%
You are still defending her?

00:12:28.930 --> 00:12:29.770 line:80%
Careful.

00:12:35.290 --> 00:12:36.220 line:80%
Steps.

00:12:37.380 --> 00:12:38.220 line:80%
Take my hand.

00:12:38.530 --> 00:12:39.370 line:80%
First step.

00:12:39.980 --> 00:12:40.820 line:80%
Second.

00:12:59.220 --> 00:13:00.060 line:80%
There.

00:13:04.660 --> 00:13:05.900 line:80%
(Peach Blossom Tavern)

00:13:05.900 --> 00:13:06.980 line:80%
I promised you, remember?

00:13:07.290 --> 00:13:09.290 line:80%
I'd share my childhood with you.

00:13:16.690 --> 00:13:17.530 line:80%
Look.

00:13:17.900 --> 00:13:19.450 line:80%
(Nutritious Pastry)
This is the pastry shop.

00:13:20.170 --> 00:13:21.100 line:80%
Their peach blossom pastries

00:13:21.100 --> 00:13:22.100 line:80%
are the best.

00:13:22.540 --> 00:13:23.450 line:80%
(Ingenious Study)

00:13:23.450 --> 00:13:24.330 line:80%
And next door

00:13:24.330 --> 00:13:25.860 line:80%
is Ingenious Scholar's shop.

00:13:25.860 --> 00:13:28.330 line:80%
There are so many storybooks there.

00:13:28.330 --> 00:13:29.530 line:80%
There's this one mysterious little box,

00:13:30.290 --> 00:13:32.380 line:80%
with books they'd never let kids touch.

00:13:36.020 --> 00:13:36.860 line:80%
See this?

00:13:37.810 --> 00:13:38.980 line:80%
We're catching ants.

00:13:43.740 --> 00:13:44.580 line:80%
That's me?

00:13:46.450 --> 00:13:47.980 line:80%
I said I'd share half with you,

00:13:48.330 --> 00:13:49.450 line:80%
so you have to be here for it.

00:14:00.650 --> 00:14:01.740 line:80%
The past

00:14:02.570 --> 00:14:03.450 line:80%
is behind us.

00:14:04.330 --> 00:14:05.380 line:80%
From now on,

00:14:06.170 --> 00:14:08.170 line:80%
I just want you to be happy.

00:14:09.860 --> 00:14:11.500 line:80%
You have a beautiful smile.

00:14:11.500 --> 00:14:12.450 line:80%
You should use it more.

00:14:17.100 --> 00:14:19.410 line:80%
And pay more attention to the people
around you.

00:14:20.140 --> 00:14:20.980 line:80%
I believe

00:14:21.740 --> 00:14:23.100 line:80%
that without those Sevens Pills,

00:14:24.140 --> 00:14:25.980 line:80%
You Guanyue and the others still wouldn't
turn on you.

00:14:26.930 --> 00:14:28.100 line:80%
You don't need to test people

00:14:28.740 --> 00:14:29.740 line:80%
with life and death

00:14:30.330 --> 00:14:32.020 line:80%
to earn real loyalty.

00:14:38.310 --> 00:14:39.170 line:80%
Zhao.

00:14:39.170 --> 00:14:40.010 line:80%
Mu Qingyan,

00:14:41.530 --> 00:14:42.370 line:80%
I love you.

00:14:44.650 --> 00:14:45.620 line:80%
I love you

00:14:46.930 --> 00:14:48.290 line:80%
very much.

00:14:50.100 --> 00:14:51.380 line:80%
No matter whether you

00:14:51.900 --> 00:14:52.740 line:80%
deceived me,

00:14:53.900 --> 00:14:54.740 line:80%
or even lost your mind,

00:14:57.690 --> 00:14:59.290 line:80%
I can't stop myself

00:14:59.290 --> 00:15:00.290 line:80%
from loving you.

00:15:02.690 --> 00:15:03.860 line:80%
I love you so much

00:15:05.450 --> 00:15:08.020 line:80%
that I once thought of giving you
everything I have.

00:15:09.170 --> 00:15:11.220 line:80%
I want to know every part of you.

00:15:12.690 --> 00:15:14.170 line:80%
I love you too much to lie to you.

00:15:15.450 --> 00:15:16.930 line:80%
I love you enough that I can't watch you

00:15:17.690 --> 00:15:19.380 line:80%
walk the same road as Mu Zhengyang.

00:15:21.020 --> 00:15:21.860 line:80%
The truth is,

00:15:22.620 --> 00:15:24.860 line:80%
even if I had known your plan
from the very beginning,

00:15:29.170 --> 00:15:30.620 line:80%
I still would have chosen to save you.

00:15:32.740 --> 00:15:33.930 line:80%
You're afraid

00:15:35.980 --> 00:15:36.900 line:80%
of the dark.

00:15:38.500 --> 00:15:39.740 line:80%
All that power,

00:15:40.980 --> 00:15:42.450 line:80%
and you trust no one.

00:15:44.620 --> 00:15:46.380 line:80%
If they crippled your cultivation,

00:15:48.450 --> 00:15:49.290 line:80%
I can't imagine

00:15:52.380 --> 00:15:54.050 line:80%
how you'd survive.

00:15:55.170 --> 00:15:56.410 line:80%
But a path paved with corpses

00:15:57.900 --> 00:15:59.500 line:80%
is not the way home.

00:16:03.690 --> 00:16:05.570 line:80%
It'll just leave you with nothing.

00:16:07.020 --> 00:16:08.290 line:80%
I don't want to be locked away.

00:16:10.740 --> 00:16:13.500 line:80%
And I don't want you locked away either.

00:16:19.410 --> 00:16:20.250 line:80%
Mu Qingyan,

00:16:23.900 --> 00:16:25.140 line:80%
I have to go home.

00:16:35.330 --> 00:16:36.170 line:80%
Zhao.

00:17:01.530 --> 00:17:02.370 line:80%
Miss Cai!

00:17:02.780 --> 00:17:03.620 line:80%
Miss Cai!

00:17:03.780 --> 00:17:05.050 line:80%
We found a wedding dress shop!

00:17:13.530 --> 00:17:14.570 line:80%
Miss Cai!

00:17:14.850 --> 00:17:15.690 line:80%
Master You.

00:17:25.430 --> 00:17:26.290 line:80%
Young Master.

00:17:26.290 --> 00:17:27.130 line:80%
Where's Miss Cai?

00:17:29.050 --> 00:17:29.980 line:80%
She left.

00:17:29.980 --> 00:17:30.820 line:80%
She's gone?

00:17:31.530 --> 00:17:32.370 line:80%
I'll bring her back.

00:17:32.370 --> 00:17:33.210 line:80%
Don't.

00:17:35.530 --> 00:17:36.570 line:80%
She won't come back.

00:17:56.180 --> 00:17:57.090 line:80%
Yuzhi.

00:17:57.420 --> 00:17:58.980 line:80%
You have the nerve to come back?!

00:17:58.980 --> 00:18:00.290 line:80%
Father was good to you!

00:18:00.290 --> 00:18:01.740 line:80%
And you shamelessly schemed with
that demon sect!

00:18:01.740 --> 00:18:03.610 line:80%
You betrayed your master, your sect, for a man!

00:18:03.610 --> 00:18:04.450 line:80%
You...

00:18:06.810 --> 00:18:08.090 line:80%
What happens to Zhao

00:18:08.610 --> 00:18:10.090 line:80%
should be decided by the lords.

00:18:12.460 --> 00:18:13.330 line:80%
It's good you are back.

00:18:13.780 --> 00:18:14.620 line:80%
It's good.

00:18:15.460 --> 00:18:16.930 line:80%
Zhao, Master's waiting.

00:18:20.460 --> 00:18:21.300 line:80%
Stop.

00:19:09.420 --> 00:19:11.300 line:80%
(Righteous Spirit)

00:19:13.500 --> 00:19:14.570 line:80%
My aunt's Sunshine Blade

00:19:15.370 --> 00:19:16.850 line:80%
was meant for slaying demons.

00:19:17.610 --> 00:19:18.500 line:80%
I'm not worthy to wield it.

00:19:29.290 --> 00:19:31.220 line:80%
Grandfather forged this Heart-Protect Chain
for me,

00:19:31.780 --> 00:19:33.290 line:80%
and I used it to save someone from
the demon sect.

00:19:34.050 --> 00:19:35.330 line:80%
I'm not worthy of this either.

00:19:41.700 --> 00:19:43.130 line:80%
Zhao. Zhao!

00:19:43.130 --> 00:19:43.970 line:80%
No, no, don't.

00:19:45.020 --> 00:19:45.890 line:80%
I, Cai Zhao, have betrayed

00:19:46.180 --> 00:19:47.020 line:80%
my master and sect,

00:19:47.420 --> 00:19:48.460 line:80%
colluded with the Demon Sect,

00:19:48.890 --> 00:19:49.810 line:80%
maimed my fellow disciples, and

00:19:50.740 --> 00:19:51.610 line:80%
shown disrespect to my elders.

00:19:52.740 --> 00:19:53.780 line:80%
My crimes are unforgivable.

00:19:54.220 --> 00:19:55.460 line:80%
Today, I sincerely plead guilty.

00:19:55.890 --> 00:19:56.940 line:80%
Whatever punishment is decreed,

00:19:58.290 --> 00:19:59.130 line:80%
I am willing

00:19:59.610 --> 00:20:00.610 line:80%
to accept it without complaint.

00:20:02.220 --> 00:20:03.060 line:80%
Cai Zhao,

00:20:04.050 --> 00:20:05.530 line:80%
are you sure about this?

00:20:12.530 --> 00:20:13.890 line:80%
Cai Zhao, traitorous disciple

00:20:14.500 --> 00:20:15.340 line:80%
of Qingque Sect,

00:20:16.020 --> 00:20:17.700 line:80%
receive your sentence. Accept your punishment.

00:20:20.370 --> 00:20:21.370 line:80%
Betrayal of master and sect,

00:20:21.940 --> 00:20:22.810 line:80%
alliance with the demon sect,

00:20:23.290 --> 00:20:24.530 line:80%
defiance of all that is right,

00:20:24.940 --> 00:20:25.810 line:80%
those are unforgivable crimes.

00:20:26.420 --> 00:20:27.260 line:80%
It is only fitting

00:20:27.660 --> 00:20:28.740 line:80%
that the sect be cleansed of her.

00:20:31.180 --> 00:20:32.660 line:80%
I'd like to see

00:20:32.660 --> 00:20:33.980 line:80%
who dares touch my daughter!

00:20:36.220 --> 00:20:37.220 line:80%
Lord Cai.

00:20:37.220 --> 00:20:38.060 line:80%
Please calm down.

00:20:38.660 --> 00:20:41.020 line:80%
No one died because of what she did.

00:20:41.700 --> 00:20:43.290 line:80%
Just strip her cultivation and be done with it.

00:20:44.130 --> 00:20:45.810 line:80%
Strip her cultivation?

00:20:45.810 --> 00:20:48.290 line:80%
What young person doesn't make mistakes?

00:20:48.290 --> 00:20:49.130 line:80%
If you ask me,

00:20:49.130 --> 00:20:50.890 line:80%
just let it go.

00:20:51.500 --> 00:20:53.290 line:80%
Let Lord Cai take her home

00:20:53.290 --> 00:20:54.460 line:80%
and deal with it privately.

00:20:55.500 --> 00:20:56.420 line:80%
A household has its rules.

00:20:56.850 --> 00:20:58.020 line:80%
A sect has its laws.

00:20:59.220 --> 00:21:01.740 line:80%
If Cai Zhao walks away from this lightly,

00:21:02.130 --> 00:21:04.020 line:80%
what's to stop other disciples

00:21:04.020 --> 00:21:05.020 line:80%
from doing the same?

00:21:05.700 --> 00:21:06.740 line:80%
Should we just

00:21:07.290 --> 00:21:08.370 line:80%
let them off easy too?

00:21:09.460 --> 00:21:10.330 line:80%
Li Wenxun,

00:21:10.330 --> 00:21:11.330 line:80%
what do you want?

00:21:13.370 --> 00:21:16.180 line:80%
Seven lashes from the Bone-Piercing
Python Whip.

00:21:16.740 --> 00:21:17.610 line:80%
After that,

00:21:17.610 --> 00:21:19.290 line:80%
confinement at the Thousandfold Cliff

00:21:19.610 --> 00:21:20.660 line:80%
to reflect on her mistakes.

00:21:20.660 --> 00:21:21.500 line:80%
No!

00:21:22.500 --> 00:21:23.530 line:80%
Can anyone

00:21:23.530 --> 00:21:25.180 line:80%
survive that Python Whip?

00:21:25.180 --> 00:21:26.290 line:80%
Enough. Stop talking.

00:21:26.290 --> 00:21:27.130 line:80%
Alright.

00:21:27.530 --> 00:21:28.370 line:80%
Zhao.

00:21:29.020 --> 00:21:29.940 line:80%
Mother.

00:21:29.940 --> 00:21:31.130 line:80%
I made a grave mistake.

00:21:33.090 --> 00:21:33.930 line:80%
I deserve this.

00:21:40.700 --> 00:21:41.980 line:80%
After the punishment,

00:21:43.810 --> 00:21:45.090 line:80%
no one speaks of this again.

00:21:45.740 --> 00:21:47.090 line:80%
Mu Qingyan nearly killed my son.

00:21:47.090 --> 00:21:48.460 line:80%
This is too lenient.

00:21:48.460 --> 00:21:49.300 line:80%
You, Yang.

00:21:50.180 --> 00:21:51.890 line:80%
If it weren't for Cai Pingshu back then,

00:21:51.890 --> 00:21:53.370 line:80%
your entire family would've been

00:21:53.370 --> 00:21:55.570 line:80%
turned into corpse slaves by Nie Hengcheng.

00:21:55.570 --> 00:21:57.290 line:80%
Learn some mercy,

00:21:57.290 --> 00:21:58.610 line:80%
you ungrateful mongrel.

00:21:58.980 --> 00:21:59.820 line:80%
- Wenxun!
- You...

00:22:00.610 --> 00:22:01.450 line:80%
Present the whip.

00:22:03.850 --> 00:22:04.850 line:80%
As Sect Chief,

00:22:05.700 --> 00:22:06.940 line:80%
I will carry this out myself.

00:23:58.740 --> 00:24:00.330 line:80%
Execute!

00:25:15.370 --> 00:25:17.020 line:80%
First lash!

00:25:51.810 --> 00:25:53.290 line:80%
Second lash!

00:26:12.940 --> 00:26:14.460 line:80%
Third lash!

00:26:29.220 --> 00:26:30.180 line:80%
She's just a child.

00:26:30.180 --> 00:26:31.020 line:80%
This is how you train her?

00:26:31.660 --> 00:26:33.090 line:80%
When we became sworn brother and sister,

00:26:33.090 --> 00:26:34.810 line:80%
I never pegged you for such a softie.

00:26:36.780 --> 00:26:37.660 line:80%
Zhao.

00:26:37.660 --> 00:26:38.850 line:80%
Let's go. No more training.

00:26:39.530 --> 00:26:40.370 line:80%
I'll buy you candy.

00:26:42.980 --> 00:26:45.090 line:80%
Candy! Candy!

00:26:45.090 --> 00:26:45.930 line:80%
Yes.

00:26:45.940 --> 00:26:47.570 line:80%
- Let's get candy!
- Candy!

00:26:47.570 --> 00:26:48.850 line:80%
- Let's go!
- Buy candy.

00:26:49.180 --> 00:26:50.620 line:80%
Candy!

00:26:50.620 --> 00:26:52.660 line:80%
- Let's get candy!
- I love candy!

00:27:03.610 --> 00:27:06.050 line:80%
Fourth lash!

00:27:51.890 --> 00:27:53.330 line:80%
Fifth lash!

00:28:01.720 --> 00:28:02.570 line:80%
- Don't!
- Zhao!

00:28:02.570 --> 00:28:03.410 line:80%
You can't go.

00:28:03.410 --> 00:28:04.610 line:80%
No, you can't.

00:28:29.130 --> 00:28:31.420 line:80%
Sixth lash!

00:28:44.500 --> 00:28:46.780 line:80%
I loved Yellow so much.

00:28:46.780 --> 00:28:48.780 line:80%
Why did he bite me?

00:28:48.780 --> 00:28:51.980 line:80%
I will never love a dog again.

00:28:57.780 --> 00:28:58.620 line:80%
Zhao.

00:28:59.020 --> 00:29:00.180 line:80%
Loving isn't wrong.

00:29:01.290 --> 00:29:03.290 line:80%
If you find out you love the wrong thing,

00:29:03.780 --> 00:29:05.610 line:80%
figure it out and set it right.

00:29:06.460 --> 00:29:08.460 line:80%
There's so much beauty in this world.

00:29:09.090 --> 00:29:10.850 line:80%
Don't let fear stop you

00:29:10.850 --> 00:29:11.940 line:80%
from loving.

00:29:12.420 --> 00:29:13.260 line:80%
Okay?

00:30:11.330 --> 00:30:13.050 line:80%
Seventh lash!

00:30:20.370 --> 00:30:21.220 line:80%
Zhao!

00:31:15.780 --> 00:31:16.660 line:80%
Zhao!

00:32:53.020 --> 00:32:54.850 line:80%
Qi Yunke didn't hold back at all.

00:32:55.810 --> 00:32:57.500 line:80%
Zhao is just a girl,

00:32:57.500 --> 00:32:58.890 line:80%
and he beat her so hard.

00:32:59.460 --> 00:33:00.940 line:80%
And now she's locked away in the Realm Cavern

00:33:00.940 --> 00:33:02.130 line:80%
for a whole year,

00:33:03.050 --> 00:33:04.290 line:80%
no visits, no news.

00:33:05.500 --> 00:33:06.850 line:80%
Stop pacing.

00:33:06.850 --> 00:33:08.330 line:80%
We don't even know how she's doing.

00:33:09.090 --> 00:33:10.610 line:80%
Just stop nagging.

00:33:12.610 --> 00:33:13.890 line:80%
All the sect chiefs were there.

00:33:14.330 --> 00:33:16.530 line:80%
Yunke is the head of the Six Sects.

00:33:17.420 --> 00:33:18.740 line:80%
He already allowed Feicui

00:33:19.130 --> 00:33:20.570 line:80%
to tend her wounds.

00:33:21.500 --> 00:33:22.780 line:80%
Stop complaining.

00:33:22.780 --> 00:33:23.780 line:80%
He already made an exception,

00:33:24.290 --> 00:33:25.420 line:80%
letting Yuzhi look after her.

00:33:25.740 --> 00:33:26.580 line:80%
I believe that Yuzhi

00:33:27.180 --> 00:33:28.290 line:80%
will do everything he can

00:33:28.980 --> 00:33:29.890 line:80%
to take care of Zhao.

00:33:30.290 --> 00:33:31.460 line:80%
Then we'll have to

00:33:31.460 --> 00:33:32.610 line:80%
rely on Yuzhi for that.

00:33:33.100 --> 00:33:34.820 line:80%
(Righteous Spirit)

00:33:39.050 --> 00:33:39.890 line:80%
I've prepared medicine.

00:33:40.370 --> 00:33:41.980 line:80%
Zhao will recover once she takes it.

00:33:41.980 --> 00:33:42.820 line:80%
No need.

00:33:43.530 --> 00:33:44.570 line:80%
Those seven lashes

00:33:44.570 --> 00:33:45.850 line:80%
damaged her meridians.

00:33:45.850 --> 00:33:47.050 line:80%
No medicine can fix that.

00:33:47.050 --> 00:33:48.290 line:80%
Enough.

00:33:48.290 --> 00:33:49.130 line:80%
Xiaofeng.

00:33:49.290 --> 00:33:51.610 line:80%
This is brewed from the Withered Branch.

00:33:52.740 --> 00:33:53.740 line:80%
The Withered Branch?

00:33:59.810 --> 00:34:01.700 line:80%
The one Pingshu planted?

00:34:03.090 --> 00:34:04.290 line:80%
All these years,

00:34:04.290 --> 00:34:06.020 line:80%
Lord Qi has been draining his inner power

00:34:06.020 --> 00:34:07.180 line:80%
trying to heal Pingshu's injuries.

00:34:08.330 --> 00:34:10.410 line:80%
He was waiting for this branch to bloom

00:34:10.410 --> 00:34:11.370 line:80%
to use the flower as medicine.

00:34:11.370 --> 00:34:12.210 line:80%
Enough said.

00:34:12.700 --> 00:34:15.290 line:80%
This was always meant for Zhao.

00:34:16.180 --> 00:34:17.140 line:80%
Take it to Yuzhi.

00:34:17.450 --> 00:34:18.620 line:80%
Tell him to give it to her.

00:34:30.620 --> 00:34:36.100 line:80%
(Realm Cavern)

00:35:09.330 --> 00:35:10.170 line:80%
Zhao.

00:35:13.450 --> 00:35:14.290 line:80%
Yuzhi.

00:35:15.970 --> 00:35:16.850 line:80%
Drink this,

00:35:17.540 --> 00:35:18.380 line:80%
and the pain will fade.

00:35:31.290 --> 00:35:32.370 line:80%
Thank you, Yuzhi.

00:35:34.100 --> 00:35:34.940 line:80%
Zhao,

00:35:35.890 --> 00:35:36.930 line:80%
if it hurts, cry.

00:35:38.850 --> 00:35:39.690 line:80%
I'm here.

00:35:40.060 --> 00:35:41.100 line:80%
I'll stay with you.

00:35:44.700 --> 00:35:45.540 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:35:48.620 --> 00:35:50.290 line:80%
I just need some rest.

00:35:58.370 --> 00:36:00.410 line:80%
Now that Nie Zhe is dead,

00:36:00.410 --> 00:36:02.890 line:80%
Young Master, what are your plans?

00:36:03.450 --> 00:36:04.930 line:80%
But the man in black behind him
is still out there.

00:36:06.370 --> 00:36:07.620 line:80%
If we don't deal with him,

00:36:08.410 --> 00:36:09.890 line:80%
he'll become a real threat.

00:36:10.000 --> 00:36:10.890 line:80%
Young Master,

00:36:10.890 --> 00:36:11.730 line:80%
this time

00:36:12.010 --> 00:36:14.780 line:80%
Miss Cai took seven lashes from
the Python Whip.

00:36:15.740 --> 00:36:16.810 line:80%
She'll live,

00:36:17.330 --> 00:36:18.490 line:80%
but those wounds

00:36:18.850 --> 00:36:20.220 line:80%
take time to heal.

00:36:21.060 --> 00:36:23.010 line:80%
Lord Qi has confined he

00:36:23.010 --> 00:36:26.740 line:80%
to the Realm Cavern at the Thousandfold Cliff

00:36:27.290 --> 00:36:28.540 line:80%
for a year of solitary reflection.

00:36:30.410 --> 00:36:31.450 line:80%
In this future year,

00:36:32.370 --> 00:36:33.620 line:80%
only Song Yuzhi

00:36:33.970 --> 00:36:35.100 line:80%
is allowed in or out

00:36:35.410 --> 00:36:36.250 line:80%
to tend to her.

00:36:36.780 --> 00:36:38.290 line:80%
From now on, she is her,

00:36:38.290 --> 00:36:39.130 line:80%
and I am me.

00:36:39.780 --> 00:36:41.540 line:80%
From now on, throughout the Li Sect,

00:36:41.540 --> 00:36:43.810 line:80%
no one speaks of her again.

00:36:47.200 --> 00:36:57.860 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:37:16.620 --> 00:37:21.030 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

00:37:21.595 --> 00:37:26.210 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

00:37:26.550 --> 00:37:31.115 line:80%
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

00:37:31.640 --> 00:37:35.940 line:80%
♪Free to wander in the world♪

00:37:38.885 --> 00:37:43.585 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:37:44.110 --> 00:37:48.400 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:37:49.060 --> 00:37:53.090 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:37:53.405 --> 00:37:58.530 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:37:59.105 --> 00:38:03.915 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:38:04.130 --> 00:38:08.300 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:38:09.025 --> 00:38:12.960 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:38:13.460 --> 00:38:18.735 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

00:38:41.465 --> 00:38:46.595 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:38:46.960 --> 00:38:51.330 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:38:51.595 --> 00:38:55.725 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:38:55.910 --> 00:39:01.485 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪